<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="18Nov1936"><font color="red">18 November 1936</font> <i>NLHW</i> (from Paul L&eacute;on to Harriet Weaver): Mr Joyce &hellip; black &hellip; total solitude &hellip; For the moment he is working hard and I believe that the book will be ready within a year. </div>
